Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.43,0:00:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明与黑暗\N在陷入一片混乱的战国时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.33,0:00:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了四魂之玉\N因缘际会聚在一起的伙伴们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越五百年的时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.27,0:00:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最后仅存的四魂之玉碎片\N引导着各自的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.57,0:00:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战国时代的传奇故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.97,0:00:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.54,0:00:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的妖马  炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.45,0:00:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说只要骑上它的人\N可以取得天下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.18,0:00:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在它被解开了封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.08,0:00:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且它的背后有着\N奈落的分身婴儿跟神乐的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.35,0:00:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can now dream（勇敢的梦想）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.19,0:00:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥起舞动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.42,0:00:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a world（暧昧的世界）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.09,0:00:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋力冲出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.81,0:00:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对忧郁的现实生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.78,0:00:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断在心中自我成长的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.78,0:01:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜的梦境及梦中残留的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.79,0:01:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断断续续提醒我“勇往直前”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.06,0:01:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破茧而出的我  及含苞待放的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.70,0:01:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就将它禁锢起来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.81,0:01:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can now dream（勇敢的梦想）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥起舞动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.84,0:01:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go in and try（不顾一切的去尝试）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.18,0:01:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.35,0:01:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你天长地久永不分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.85,0:01:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need to cry（同样的哭泣）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.16,0:01:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孤独相伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.79,0:01:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show me a day fight（直接应战）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.16,0:01:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当伤心流泪的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.36,0:01:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它成为坚定不移的梦想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是心理作用吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.32,0:02:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.09,0:02:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.16,0:02:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我安份点\N马上就会结束的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风刃之舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第141话 被释放的妖马炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.64,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.58,0:03:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不是才吃过鱼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.28,0:03:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又没有吃到饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.59,0:03:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不介意的话\N就交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带着什么吃的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N我是没有带什么啦  不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.83,0:03:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是村子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.03,0:03:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  那就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.74,0:04:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有饭吃了\N吃饭  吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得有点不对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个村子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神官大人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.56,0:04:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  神官大人被杀害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.83,0:04:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是指最近频传的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.19,0:04:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专门杀害那些\N道行高深的神官和僧人这件事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.43,0:04:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道\N到底是什么人干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.27,0:04:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一直发展到现在\N事情绝不寻常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因为这样\N被封印在神社里的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每到晚上就出来作乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.64,0:04:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以村子才这么荒凉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉到什么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.17,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有气味\N虽然只是杂碎妖怪的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且藏了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.98,0:05:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家可别大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我\N我一招就把他们通通解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.92,0:05:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要开动咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.08,0:05:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.71,0:05:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.84,0:05:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的事情\N在这附近经常发生是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.22,0:05:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  到处都是这样的传闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛抢我的  还我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.72,0:06:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高僧和神官\N接二连三地遭到杀害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底会是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.60,0:06:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手好像是一个\N抱着婴儿的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说  难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婴儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.97,0:06:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.74,0:06:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么听来\N那个女人想必是神乐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了这个时候\N还以人类为目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.18,0:06:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们到底想要干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情怎么样都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正如果这件事跟\N奈落那个家伙扯上关系的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就不能袖手旁观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.69,0:06:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.39,0:06:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  是这样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在神乐在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个倒不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.97,0:06:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近最有名气的僧人\N或神官是哪一位呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是问还在世的高僧吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.78,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近还活着的高僧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来最有名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.49,0:07:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是万愿寺的神泉和尚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神泉和尚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指那位神泉和尚吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听过他的名字吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.03,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N是一位很有名的僧人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.03,0:07:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说论起封印妖怪的功力\N无人能出其右啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.37,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连身为驱魔师的我也听说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是非常有名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.38,0:07:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是封印了那个\N人称炼狱鬼的食人妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.55,0:07:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及他骑的妖马“炎蹄”\N这个传说是最为有名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问您怎么了吗  神泉师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…可能是我多疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.71,0:08:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像感觉到炎蹄在嘶鸣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎蹄?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.05,0:08:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是封印在\N我们后山祠堂的妖马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.05,0:08:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎蹄正如其名\N是一匹有着火焰马蹄的马妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也是传说中能够日行千里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚力非凡的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.43,0:08:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.43,0:08:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相隔百年前有一匹神马\N被卷入大火之中死去的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.40,0:08:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的怨灵出现在这个世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.17,0:08:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且随着火山爆发\N转生成为炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.31,0:08:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  都还不清楚咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.42,0:08:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.45,0:08:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过传说还不只是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.96,0:08:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于炎蹄还有另外一个传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.96,0:08:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑上炎蹄的话\N就能够取得天下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道是什么人传开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这种说法广为流传
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.60,0:09:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然这种说法\N只不过是一种迷信罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.24,0:09:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类跟妖怪之间的争斗\N却没有停止过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.88,0:09:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过了跟人类与妖怪\N无数次的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后生存下来的炼狱鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎蹄给予他骑上它的权利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是得到了炎蹄的炼狱鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得气势逼人狂暴无比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为炼狱鬼的四处作乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.37,0:09:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而让村民们感到痛苦不堪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.24,0:09:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是拜托了神泉和尚\N为他们驱魔除妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.62,0:09:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我跟炼狱鬼的战斗\N持续了三天三夜的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.62,0:10:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且为了要封印炎蹄\N耗个三天三夜也是必要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.66,0:10:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易\N打败了这两个妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.29,0:10:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且分别封印在\N两个不同的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个祠堂也就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.27,0:10:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在说起来\N已经是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.04,0:10:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神泉和尚能够打败\N如此厉害妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一位非常了不起的高僧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.58,0:10:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是预感…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.12,0:11:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过既然是能够\N封印那种妖怪的和尚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.42,0:11:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐会盯上他\N也没什么好奇怪的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.22,0:11:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N既然如此我们快点出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间在这里磨蹭下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.61,0:11:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?快点去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.71,0:11:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦  真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爱使唤别人的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.58,0:11:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神泉师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么地方不对劲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都没有感觉到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座寺庙的附近\N有邪气正在逼近当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快点去躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.03,0:11:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.27,0:11:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟之前的那些家伙比起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.84,0:11:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像稍微厉害了一点嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.17,0:11:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现身吧  妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以为是的布下结界了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.28,0:12:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说杀害高僧的妖怪\N是个抱着婴儿的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.65,0:12:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们杀害了\N那些僧人跟神官的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个婴儿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.43,0:12:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个女人\N恐怕还要凶恶好几倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.87,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许这和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.17,0:12:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我窥视到\N此世与彼世的交界处吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.78,0:12:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚  下一招你还避得开吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.08,0:12:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风刃之舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.18,0:12:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.55,0:12:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两下子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.56,0:12:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这一招又如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙蛇之舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神泉师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.67,0:12:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的  什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.33,0:13:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神泉师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好好地来窥视你的心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.86,0:13:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成…功了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…毕竟也老了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.47,0:14:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神泉师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.14,0:14:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子…恐怕不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.15,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有血的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还很新鲜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上有香的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事的地点恐怕是寺庙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.93,0:14:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神乐下的手吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还留有那家伙的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手的\N是一个抱着婴儿的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.94,0:14:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有说错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.68,0:14:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父很勇敢地\N跟那个妖怪战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜为了保护\N我们两个人的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.69,0:14:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易\N把两个妖怪其中一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.45,0:14:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个婴儿成功地消灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.30,0:15:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.80,0:15:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父的法力将他劈成两半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.84,0:15:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个婴儿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奈落在白灵山之中\N再次诞生出来的分身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在白灵山魔塌的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还特地带那个婴儿逃了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.68,0:15:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对奈落来说\N他应该是相当重要的存在对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.46,0:15:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  总觉得没这么简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.36,0:15:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最猛胜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.51,0:15:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想带我去什么地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神无
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奈落派你来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.42,0:16:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成\N你是代替奈落来教训我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.03,0:16:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个由神乐来保护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.91,0:16:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正迟早有一天\N会变成这个样子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窥视此世与彼世的交界处?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.29,0:16:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在杀了师父之前\N那个婴儿就是这么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么窥视心灵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.40,0:16:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐和婴儿\N到处杀害神官和高僧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.30,0:16:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来觉得是为了\N把被封印住的妖怪们给解放出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.64,0:16:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来似乎没那么简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.34,0:16:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此世与彼世的交界处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有什么东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.09,0:17:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.39,0:17:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是那个妖怪的封印吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在后山是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.56,0:17:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们师父\N好不容易用他的法力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印住的一匹\N叫做炎蹄的妖马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.83,0:17:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.93,0:17:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个叫炼狱鬼\N所骑的那匹妖马吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.04,0:17:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.64,0:17:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.31,0:17:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.64,0:17:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.37,0:17:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎蹄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少得意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.56,0:18:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒  你们也没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.43,0:18:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是犬夜叉  那匹妖马…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.63,0:18:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.63,0:18:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好跟它算个帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧  风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.41,0:18:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.84,0:18:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往这里来了  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.02,0:18:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.92,0:18:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.76,0:18:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.90,0:19:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.87,0:19:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  既然如此我就用风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.88,0:19:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘴气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.98,0:19:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  那匹马冲来冲去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.62,0:19:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太得意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.96,0:19:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.26,0:19:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别管我\N一定要想办法阻止那个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  速度太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.21,0:19:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样根本就瞄不准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点阻止\N那匹妖马的行动的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它停止移动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.38,0:19:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.42,0:19:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来你就死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候干嘛阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况不太对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.99,0:19:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  大家快跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.88,0:20:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.51,0:20:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为死定了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.22,0:21:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一定是想要去找\N被封印的主人炼狱鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.39,0:21:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快点追吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.04,0:21:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下一半\N是要我怎么处理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点气息都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.55,0:21:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.06,0:21:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你复活了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活过来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.58,0:22:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.22,0:22:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今内心充满着悲伤的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.21,0:22:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管靠着我哭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像现在这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.67,0:23:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come my way 这点黑暗之尘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.65,0:23:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come close to me 现在灯已照亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.19,0:23:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是简简单单的陪在你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.26,0:23:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是你解开妖马封印的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.49,0:23:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎蹄选择了个\N看似不祥的孩子骑在自己的背上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.46,0:23:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是白童子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.80,0:23:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们应该知道\N我也是奈落的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.33,0:23:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要窥视\N彼世与此世的交界处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.20,0:23:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.67,0:23:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一能看到的\N是白茫茫的雾世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.94,0:23:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要不要也找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.47,0:23:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是四魂之玉的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.64,0:24:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.14,0:24:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂暴的炎蹄与战栗的白童子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.01,0:24:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.01,0:24:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那么重要的事告诉他们


